listitem.para:
An API for raising events that can be observed via
@Observer methods, or method
bindings in WEB-INF/events.xml.

interpolate(String template) — scan
the template for JSF EL expressions of the form #{...}
and replace them with their evaluated values.

Allows access to a JSF UIComponent by its id
from the EL. For example, we can write 
@In("#{uiComponent['myForm:address'].value}").
